<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 03:15:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>华为推出三折智能手机，加剧与苹果在中国的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-teases-tri-fold-smartphone-raising-competition-with-apple-china-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国华为技术有限公司 (HWT.UL) 周二推出了一款三向可折叠手机，旨在凭借在中国市场广受欢迎的新外形，扩大其在全球最大智能手机市场对苹果的领先地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 02:03:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-teases-tri-fold-smartphone-raising-competition-with-apple-china-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市上涨，关注美国通胀测试和美联储会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-10/</link><description>继华尔街隔夜上涨后，亚洲股市周二扭转早盘跌幅，小幅上涨，但对中国经济依然陷入困境的担忧抑制了市场情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 01:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>在美国通胀测试之前，货币谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-with-caution-ahead-us-inflation-test-2024-09-10/</link><description>美元周二早盘持稳，日元小幅脱离一个月高点，因投资者等待美国通胀数据，并重新评估美联储下周开始大幅降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 01:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-with-caution-ahead-us-inflation-test-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>三星SDI将以8.36亿美元向中国公司出售偏光膜业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/samsung-sdi-sell-polarizing-film-business-chinese-firm-836-mln-2024-09-09/</link><description>韩国电池制造商三星SDI周二表示，已决定以1.12万亿韩元（合8.3647亿美元）的价格将其偏光膜业务出售给中国无锡恒信光电材料公司。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 23:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/samsung-sdi-sell-polarizing-film-business-chinese-firm-836-mln-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国限制与中国药明康德、华大基因开展业务的法案众议院通过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bill-restrict-business-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-passes-house-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国众议院周一通过了一项法案，旨在以国家安全为由限制与中国药明康德、华大基因和其他几家生物技术公司的业务往来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 23:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bill-restrict-business-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-passes-house-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国贸易可能扰乱市场平静</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-09/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 21:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>“中国周”即将到来，美国众议院投票禁止新的大疆无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-votes-bar-new-drones-chinese-manufacturer-dji-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国众议院周一投票禁止中国无人机制造商大疆创新的新无人机在美国运营，这是立法者本周考虑的一系列针对中国的措施之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 20:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-votes-bar-new-drones-chinese-manufacturer-dji-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国智库负责人因中国代理人指控将被引渡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/head-us-think-tank-be-extradited-china-agent-charges-2024-09-09/</link><description>检察官周一表示，去年因被控充当未经注册的中国特工而被起诉的美国智库领导人已被捕，并将在未来几周或几个月内被引渡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 17:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/head-us-think-tank-be-extradited-china-agent-charges-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织称关税往往对穷人造成更严重的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/tariffs-tend-hit-poor-harder-wto-says-2024-09-09/</link><description>世界贸易组织周一在一份报告中表示，进口关税往往会对低收入家庭造成不成比例的打击，以反击其认为的对开放市场的抵制和不断上升的保护主义。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 14:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/tariffs-tend-hit-poor-harder-wto-says-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国提议要求先进人工智能、云提供商报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-requiring-reporting-advanced-ai-cloud-providers-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国商务部周一表示，提议要求先进人工智能开发商和云计算提供商提供详细的报告要求，以确保技术安全并能够抵御网络攻击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-requiring-reporting-advanced-ai-cloud-providers-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾参议院第二次认定前市长郭爱丽藐视法庭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-senate-holds-ex-mayor-alice-guo-contempt-second-time-2024-09-09/</link><description>菲律宾前城镇市长郭爱丽周一第二次受到藐视法庭罪，此前她拒绝回答参议员提出的有关涉嫌与中国犯罪集团有联系以及两个月前她如何逃离菲律宾的问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-senate-holds-ex-mayor-alice-guo-contempt-second-time-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>在苹果 iPhone 16 发布之前，华为三折手机预订量已达 300 万部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-racks-up-3-mln-pre-orders-tri-fold-phone-before-apples-iphone-16-reveal-2024-09-09/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为的网站周一显示，其三折叠智能手机的预订量已超过 300 万部，而就在苹果推出新一代 iPhone 的几个小时前。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-racks-up-3-mln-pre-orders-tri-fold-phone-before-apples-iphone-16-reveal-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平寻求与挪威在绿色能源领域开展“友好”合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-seeks-friendly-cooperation-with-norway-green-energy-evs-2024-09-09/</link><description>国家主席习近平周一在北京对来访的挪威首相斯托雷表示，中国愿与挪威共同推动包括绿色能源在内的“友好”合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-seeks-friendly-cooperation-with-norway-green-energy-evs-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>苹果 iPhone 16 发布会展示 AI 肌肉、新款手表和 AirPods</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apples-iphone-16-will-put-ai-features-focus-2024-09-09/</link><description>苹果周一推出了人们期待已久的人工智能增强版 iPhone 16，以及具有助听功能的 AirPods，并已提交美国监管机构审查，并更新了手表。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apples-iphone-16-will-put-ai-features-focus-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：黎智英的香港媒体公司高管对 BDO 提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/execs-jimmy-lais-hong-kong-media-firm-mount-legal-challenge-against-bdo-2024-09-09/</link><description>两名在香港拥有长期经验的西方媒体高管指责国际会计师事务所BDO违反国际规则，帮助香港政府清算该公司，该公司由被监禁的大亨黎智英经营。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:46:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/execs-jimmy-lais-hong-kong-media-firm-mount-legal-challenge-against-bdo-2024-09-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>